{"title_page": "TrueCAD", "text_new": "= TrueCAD =\nTrueCAD<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://truecad.pl/|title=TrueCAD - Tw\u00f3j CAD {{!}} NOWOCZESNY {{!}} SZYBKI {{!}} EKONOMICZNY|website=truecad.pl|language=pl|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://truecad.com/|title=TrueCAD Software, IntelliCAD 9.2, 2D Drafting, 3D Modeling CAD Software|website=truecad.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref> - budget version of CAD software produced by [https://actcad.com ActCAD LLC USA]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://actcad.com/|title=ActCAD IntelliCAD Software, AutoCAD Alternative, ActCAD 2D&3D CAD Software|last=LLC|first=ActCAD|website=actcad.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>, a company belonging to the [https://intellicad.org ITC Consortium] ([[IntelliCAD|IntelliCAD Technology Consortium]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.intellicad.org/|title=Alternative CAD Platform {{!}} IntelliCAD Technology Consortium|last=Consortium|first=IntelliCAD Technology|website=www.intellicad.org|language=en|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>). TrueCAD is a commercial computer aided design software developed by ActCAD LLC USA. TrueCAD software is designed to work in a [[Microsoft Windows]] environment. TrueCAD comes from the ActCAD Standard software line, and just like it has been stripped of some third-party add-ons and prevents editing of [[ACIS]] solids.\n\nThe latest version of the Standard line software was ActCAD 2019 Standard replaced by the new TrueCAD 2019 Premium product<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.intellicad.org/articles-and-press-releases/truecad-new-product-based-on-intellicad|title=TrueCAD: New Product Based on IntelliCAD!|last=Press|first=I. T. C.|website=www.intellicad.org|language=en-us|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>.\n\nAn interesting fact is that both products were sold in parallel by ActCAD LLC USA, but they were generally not available in the same markets.\n\nThe manufacturer's intention was to create a new budget brand in the form of a TrueCAD product, independent of the product from the premium segment of ActCAD software.\n\nLike other ActCAD LLC products, TrueCAD software is used to open, view, edit and create from scratch as well as print [[DWG]] and [[AutoCAD DXF|DXF]] as well as DNG files; it is also compatible with most versions of [[.dwg|*.dwg]] and [[AutoCAD DXF|*.dxf]] files created with the help of [[AutoCAD]].\n\nIn addition to IntelliCAD, TrueCAD also uses [[Open Design Alliance]] ([[Open Design Alliance|ODA]]) libraries and some ACIS programming tools (3DS).\n\nTrueCAD as software based on the same IntelliCAD Technology Consortium solutions as ActCAD, has an open architecture that allows the creation and customization of own extension modules by other software producers. \n\n15 language versions are available with TrueCAD, including is also available in English, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, Czech, French, Spanish, Dutch, Japanese, Korean, German, Polish, Portuguese, Russian, Serbian, Turkish, Italian.\n\nTrueCAD is used in technical and engineering fields, including by architects, builders, designers, electronics, water and sewage<span class=\"tlid-translation-gender-indicator translation-gender-indicator\"></span> plumbers, mechanics and surveyors. This may be due to the fact that there are a large number of specialized \"overlays\" working with products based on IntelliCAD solutions, which transfer between different products o<span class=\"tlid-translation-gender-indicator translation-gender-indicator\"></span>f [https://members.intellicad.org/members/index.php IntelliCAD Consortium members] is quite simple.\n\nLike other ActCAD products, TrueCAD uses [[Hardware acceleration|hardware accelerated]] [[OpenGL]] graphics technology.\n\nIt currently does not have [[DirectX]] hardware acceleration support.\n\nFor licensing reasons, TrueCAD softw<span class=\"tlid-translation-gender-indicator translation-gender-indicator\"></span>are is available in an independent distribution channel than ActCAD software.\n\n== Overlays available ==\nActCAD software works, among others, with industry overlays of the following companies: CADprofi<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://e-cadprofi.com/|title=CADprofi eShop|website=e-cadprofi.com|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref> construction, CubicOrb<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cubicorb.com/|title=Home|website=Cubic Orb|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref> geodetic (formerly Geox) or TojoCAD geodetic.\n\n== Software versions ==\n\n* TrueCAD 2019 Premium - based on the IntelliCAD 8.4B engine available for Windows Vista/7/8/8.1/10 in 32<span class=\"tlid-translation-gender-indicator translation-gender-indicator\"></span>/64bit version\n* TrueCAD 2020 Premium - based on the IntelliCAD 9.1 engine available for Windows Vista /7/8/8.1/10 in the 32/64bit version\n* TrueCAD 2020 Premium - based on the IntelliCAD 9.2 engine available for Windows Vista /7/8/8.1/10 in the 32/64bit version<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.intellicad.org/articles-and-press-releases/truecad-2020-premium-released|title=TrueCAD 2020 Premium Released|last=Press|first=I. T. C.|website=www.intellicad.org|language=en-us|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>\n\n== Supported platforms ==\nHardware requirements of the latest version:\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 Operating system:\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Microsoft\u00ae Windows\u00ae Vista (32-bit and 64-bit) or\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Microsoft\u00ae Windows\u00ae 7 (32-bit and 64-bit) or\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Microsoft\u00ae Windows\u00ae 8 / 8.1 (32-bit and 64-bit) or\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Microsoft\u00ae Windows\u00ae 10 (32-bit and 64-bit)\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 Processor:\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Minimum: 2 GHz Dual core or newer\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Recommended: at least 3 GHz i3 or newer\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 RAM:\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Minimum: at least 2GB\n\n\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Recommended: 4GB\n\nIt is possible to run the program on emulators such as [[Microsoft virtual pc|Microsoft Virtual PC]], [[VirtualBox]] or [[Wine (software)|Wine]].\n\n== References ==\n", "text_old": "= TrueCAD =\n{{Oprogramowanie infobox\n | nazwa               = TrueCAD Premium\n | rodzaj              = [[Komputerowe wspomaganie projektowania]] [[Oprogramowanie CAD/CAM]]\n | logo                = Logo TrueCAD.png\n | grafika             = \n | autor               = ActCAD LLC USA\n | platforma sprz\u0119towa = [[x86]] [[AMD64]] [[x86-64]]\n | system operacyjny   = [[Microsoft Windows]]\n | j\u0119zyk programowania = C++\n | pierwsze wydanie    = {{Dts|05|08|2018}}\n | license            =  Closed\n | commons             = \n | www                 = https://truecad.com\n}}\nTrueCAD<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://truecad.pl/|title=TrueCAD - Tw\u00f3j CAD {{!}} NOWOCZESNY {{!}} SZYBKI {{!}} EKONOMICZNY|website=truecad.pl|language=pl|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://truecad.com/|title=TrueCAD Software, IntelliCAD 9.2, 2D Drafting, 3D Modeling CAD Software|website=truecad.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref> - budget version of CAD software produced by [https://actcad.com ActCAD LLC USA]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://actcad.com/|title=ActCAD IntelliCAD Software, AutoCAD Alternative, ActCAD 2D&3D CAD Software|last=LLC|first=ActCAD|website=actcad.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>, a company belonging to the [https://intellicad.org ITC Consortium] ([[IntelliCAD|IntelliCAD Technology Consortium]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.intellicad.org/|title=Alternative CAD Platform {{!}} IntelliCAD Technology Consortium|last=Consortium|first=IntelliCAD Technology|website=www.intellicad.org|language=en|access-date=2020-04-23}}</ref>). TrueCAD is a commercial computer aided design software developed by ActCAD LLC USA. TrueCAD software is designed to work in a [[Microsoft Windows]] environment. TrueCAD comes from the ActCAD Standard software line, and just like it has been stripped of some third-party add-ons and prevents editing o